{"root":{"data":{"id":"djmsnbljwao0","created":1782864298058,"text":"SOP相关"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmue5d33yg0","created":1782869221428,"text":"备注","layout_mind_offset":{"x":-52.99999842047674,"y":159.99999523162865}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmuh4q0s5s0","created":1782869455125,"text":"lk抬头里面的","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmufgl0h7c0","created":1782869324216,"text":"确保部件开料平整，没有粗糙。否则，油第⼀次粘合剂或底油前需要打磨或打砂，以使部件表⾯平整光滑。","layout_right_offset":{"x":5.750011395662511,"y":-34.24999940767901}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djmujd80v6g0","created":1782869630357,"text":"所有部位及物料上必须使用粘合剂。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djmujneny400","created":1782869652526,"text":"所有油好边油的部件需要至少自然干2至3小时，才可进行下一个生产工序。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djmuk63ehg80","created":1782869693204,"text":"完成油边后，如果成品在正常天气条件下（~25-35℃，RH~60-70％）晾干，建议在24-48小时后进行包装。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djmut52bl800","created":1782870396239,"text":"所有边油测试建议应在涂好边油后48小时后才进行，因为所有化工品都需要时间去作固化。尽管烘干机表面好像干了，但实则未干透固化，所以建议最好在48小时后才作包装或测试。","layout_right_offset":{"x":-4.249985191971405,"y":36.24999837949875}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmuujp3mk00","created":1782870506456,"text":"平边工艺（P2026060005）","layout_right_offset":{"x":20.74999910220498,"y":113.4999975487591}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmv15qclkw0","created":1782871024605,"text":"打磨操作时，材料应握紧且平直；打磨材料时应保持稳定且均匀的手势","layout_right_offset":{"x":16.50000189989794,"y":-12.499999441206398}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmvfe9zcq80","created":1782872140305,"text":"During the buffing operation, the material should be held firmly and straight; the gesture used to buff the material should be steady and uniform."},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmv1vbucpc0","created":1782871080325,"text":"为呈现出最佳效果，最后一次打平边时需将物料朝同一方向打2 ~ 3次；","layout_right_offset":{"x":26.249998826533556,"y":-3.7499998323619934}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmvg4p376o0","created":1782872197815,"text":"For optimal results, when buffing the edges for the last time, the material should be buffed in the same direction for 2 to 3 times."},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmv25ucprk0","created":1782871103212,"text":"由于弯角、转角圆形位置不易打磨，所以那些位置无法达到平边效果；","layout_right_offset":{"x":28.749998714774847,"y":1.2499999441205887}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmvgglu5ns0","created":1782872223740,"text":"Due to the difficulty in buffing the rounded positions of bends and corners, it is impossible to achieve a flat edge effect at those locations."},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmv2p9pdgg0","created":1782871145499,"text":"根据不同的物料及厚度，调整油边的次数；","layout_right_offset":{"x":33.74999849125766,"y":-1.7053025658242404e-13}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmvh81qq4o0","created":1782872283474,"text":"It is recommended to adjust the number of coats according to the absorption and the thickness of different material."},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmv2yfjmhc0","created":1782871165443,"text":"油边前需确保部件开料平整及贴合良好，没有胶水或杂质残留在皮边上。否则，油边前需要打磨或打砂，以使部件表面平整光滑；","layout_right_offset":{"x":32.499998547136784,"y":3.7499998323619366}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmvhwidvko0","created":1782872336724,"text":"The material edges have to be clean, smooth and well compacted. Make sure the base of component is well cut, no glue or impurities remain on the edge of the material. Otherwise, buffing or sanding is needed to make it flat and smooth before edge paint application.","layout_right_offset":{"x":9.250102131311905,"y":4.583333294010856}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmv4t4ymbk0","created":1782871310647,"text":"打平边效果前需要干燥6小时以上再进行打磨；","layout_right_offset":{"x":34.99999843537819,"y":12.499999441206455}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmvnhevh0g0","created":1782872774044,"text":"Before achieving the desired edge effect, it is necessary to dry for at least 6 hours before buffing."},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmv9xmpgc80","created":1782871712248,"text":"平边效果对于边油的要求非常严格（粘度、消泡、饱满度、打磨性）；","layout_right_offset":{"x":27.99999597668642,"y":27.499998770654315}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmvo3gczsg0","created":1782872822024,"text":"This effect has very strict requirements for edge paint (viscosity, defoaming, fullness, and polishability).","layout_right_offset":{"x":-24.999998882413024,"y":-3.749999832362164}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmvprstxpc0","created":1782872953385,"text":"边油自身的注意事项","layout_right_offset":{"x":37.49999832361948,"y":267.49998804181877}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmw0aemzs00","created":1782873777527,"text":"粘合促进剂（MK）","layout_right_offset":{"x":-13.749999385327158,"y":96.24999569728993}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmw0ed4otk0","created":1782873786143,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmw6z25xog0","created":1782874301377,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmw70e3vv40","created":1782874304276,"text":"MK-一般皮边油操作程序（PMK202601001）","layout_right_offset":{"x":18.74999916180974,"y":353.7499841861432}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmw72z216w0","created":1782874309896,"text":"对于厚度为 3mm 以上、吸收性强或纤维松散的部件，可能需要多上⼀层以上的底油/⾊油. 对于厚度为 1.5mm 以下的部件, 可以少上⼀次底油","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmw95vunfs0","created":1782874472961,"text":"For the component with thickness higher than 3mm, high absorption characteristic, loose fiber… one or more coat of primer/color edge paint before the first buffing may be necessary. For the component with thickness less than 1.5mm, 1 coat of primer may be reduced."},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmweek5gfs0","created":1782874883666,"text":"上⾯的粘度指标是针对于⼀般情况下的参考标准，由于粘度受季节温度、压强的影响会发⽣变化，我司会根据实际情况（比如⼯⼚的使⽤环境温度）来适当进⾏调整，所以，如原产地与⼯⼚当地温差⽐较⼤，粘度的误差相对也会⽐较⼤。","layout_right_offset":{"x":0,"y":6.249999720603455}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmwhf15tm00","created":1782875119787,"text":"The above viscosity standard is for general circumstances. Since the viscosity will change easily due to the influence of seasonal temperature and pressure, also we will make appropriate adjustments according to the actual situation (such as the ambient temperature in production lines), thus, if the temperature difference is large between area of origin and the factory, the deviation would be relatively larger."},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmufnkb4co0","created":1782869339411,"text":"油边","layout_mind_offset":{"x":369.999988973141,"y":-95.99999713897711}},"children":[]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}